{"tid":825483,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大家放咗工無野做不妨去幫下手","createTime":"2018-09-17T15:01:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-19T00:17:39.000Z","uid":18577,"like":33,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"fdc186012be2d6618d3ccad426f5458c677c2800","tid":825483,"uid":18577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T15:01:46.000Z","msg":"今日返咗成日工其實個心都飛左出去..唔係睇新聞就係睇連登<br />\n放咗工返到屋企換完衫..忍唔住問個fd有無野做<br />\n見到杏花邨好似要義工去執垃圾<br />\n食完野就買埋手套去<br />\n一出到地鐵站唔講以為自己去咗個荒廢咗既地方<br />\n商場無哂燈唔開不突止..周地都係垃圾<br />\n杏花邨d樓既地下全部都係濕哂既泥..好似去咗下白泥一樣<br />\n執左兩個鐘我地就太攰走咗..成鞋都係泥<br />\n衫又有..袋又有..重要十隻手指甲都滿哂泥..睇黎要膠手套先掂<br />\n但唔去到現場你係唔信可以有咗多垃圾<br />\n執極都有咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">最後只係想講清潔工人真係好辛苦</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 多謝你地每日為清潔香港既努力<br />\n屌你老母濕鳩政府咪撚再外判出去為左慳個一個幾毫啦屌你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/17/230131_0e26b2d4f95a497e2efbe25284d2e1aa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F17%2F230131_0e26b2d4f95a497e2efbe25284d2e1aa.png&h=28c6fb3e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/17/230133_f8536fa55de78a8bfac90b79a3328395.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F17%2F230133_f8536fa55de78a8bfac90b79a3328395.png&h=e3989fb6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/17/230135_3dba4d321f8295c324703afb69b66c1b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F17%2F230135_3dba4d321f8295c324703afb69b66c1b.png&h=eec0a460&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/17/230136_da5b0ceb5ba44eed2b14c554af59b326.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F17%2F230136_da5b0ceb5ba44eed2b14c554af59b326.png&h=9726b21b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/17/230138_4dec715ec79f18e7b5d8705adc01e42d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F17%2F230138_4dec715ec79f18e7b5d8705adc01e42d.png&h=a23e620c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/17/230139_5d7682de14b9d36b86a8c23e8bfd8000.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F17%2F230139_5d7682de14b9d36b86a8c23e8bfd8000.png&h=87c2cab2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/17/230140_7f0e11b87a3214b7702f2b95ed1125b3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F17%2F230140_7f0e11b87a3214b7702f2b95ed1125b3.png&h=63b20fda&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/17/230142_83e68759e12f7b2af60d7069fc7e0b62.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F17%2F230142_83e68759e12f7b2af60d7069fc7e0b62.png&h=3315d6ea&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a621c16d730f944617f711e3e010a3080fb1e4ca","tid":825483,"uid":18577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T15:02:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9ece940c79a53f9bfd9f2f79017cdd7152a829f","tid":825483,"uid":187,"like":45,"dislike":0,"score":45,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T15:05:29.000Z","msg":"清潔工人真係慘<br />\n成日比人睇唔起又辛苦<br />\n無人會讚佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n香港人好賤 仲有好多死港媽會大大聲話唔讀書就係做呢d<br />\n聽到就想打鳩個港媽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ddbfc827f571